1. Essential Live Site Sections
Hero Section: A concise intro with your name, a photo (optional but adds confidence), and a clear "Full Stack Developer" headline.
Interactive Project Gallery: The core of the site. Each project should have:
Live Demo Link: A clickable button leading to the deployed app (use Vercel, Netlify, or Render).
GitHub Link: A direct link to the public source code.
Tech Stack Badges: Visual icons for the tools used (e.g., React, Node.js, PostgreSQL).
Technical Skills: A categorized display of your proficiency (Frontend, Backend, Database, DevOps).
About/Story: A brief "About Me" that highlights your problem-solving mindset and evolution.
Call to Action: Clear links to your LinkedIn, Resume (PDF), and an active Contact Form. 
