2. High-Quality Full-Stack Examples
For inspiration on layout and interactivity, look at these standard-setting live portfolios:
Brittany Chiang: Widely considered the gold standard for a clean, professional dark-mode developer site.
Tamal Sen: Uses a "programmer aesthetic" with IDE-style backgrounds and subtle animations.
Sumit Vekariya: A minimalist design that focuses on typography and whitespace to draw attention to details.
Rafael Caferati: Great example of including specialties and contact info alongside live work. 
