3. Modern Design Trends
Minimalism: Clean layouts with consistent color schemes (often dark mode) are currently the most popular trend for developer sites.
Micro-interactions: Subtle animations on hover or scroll that make the site feel "premium" without being distracting.
Responsive Performance: High Lighthouse scores for speed and accessibility are expected of a full-stack engineer. 
